OL,3,CWelsh fire service bosses 'in denial'
OL,4,Cover issues as Senedd chair 'concerned'
OL,6,FManagers are in "denial" about the
OL,7,Fmagnitude of cultural problems at ,
OL,8,Faccording to the chair of the Senedd
OL,9,Fequality committee which is hearing
OL,10,Fevidence about how the organisations
OL,11,Fare run.
OL,13,FJenny Rathbone MS, who chairs the
OL,14,Fequality and social justice committee,
OL,15,Ftold ITV Wales she "wouldn't be able
OL,16,Fto categorically say that workers are
OL,17,Fsafe" at the country's three fire and
OL,18,Frescue services: north, south, and mid
OL,19,Fand west Wales.
