OL,6,FFor five weeks, ITV Wales has been
OL,7,Finvestigating claims of at North Wales
OL,8,FFire and Rescue Service, in the
OL,9,Faftermath of a damning report into the
OL,10,Fculture at South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService yielding 82 recommendations.
OL,13,FSeparately, Ms Rathbone and the
OL,14,Fcommittee have been hearing evidence
OL,15,Fabout the governance and
OL,16,Faccountability of Welsh fire services.
