OL,6,FShe expressed concerns over the lack
OL,7,Fof action taken to tackle bullying and
OL,8,Fharassment and said she was surprised
OL,9,Fby South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,10,FService's choice of interim chief fire
OL,11,Fofficer Stuart Millington, who along
OL,12,Fwith North Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService is facing bullying allegations
OL,14,Fat an employment tribunal. He denies
OL,15,Fthe allegations.
OL,17,F"Are concerns being listened to?"
