OL,6,FDuring our investigation into the
OL,7,Fculture in north Wales, we have heard
OL,8,Fhow staff feel like their concerns
OL,9,Fhave not been listened to.
OL,11,FRecently announcing that cultural
OL,12,Freviews would take place for both
OL,13,Fnorth and mid and west Wales services,
OL,14,FWelsh Government deputy minister for
OL,15,Fsocial partnership Hannah Blythyn also
OL,16,Fsaid she had been contacted by a
OL,17,Fnumber of people from all three of the
OL,18,Fservices with serious concerns, with
OL,19,Freview findings expected to be
OL,20,Fpublished no later than autumn this
OL,21,Fyear.
