OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Senedd's equality and
OL,7,Fsocial justice committee is due to
OL,8,Fcomplete their investigation into the
OL,9,Fgovernance arrangements at Wales' fire
OL,10,Fand rescue services and publish their
OL,11,Ffindings before the end of April.
OL,13,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV Wales,
OL,14,Fcommittee chair Ms Rathbone said: "I
OL,15,Fand the rest of the committee are all
OL,16,Fvery concerned about the situation in
OL,17,Fall three fire and rescue services.
