OL,4,Cover issues as Senedd chair 'concerned'
OL,6,F"I wouldn't be able to categorically
OL,7,Fsay that workers are safe because I
OL,8,Fdon't think any of the three
OL,9,Forganisations have really done the
OL,10,Froot-and branch grassroots analysis of
OL,11,Fthe problem.
OL,13,F"This has been bubbling away for at
OL,14,Fleast 10 years.
OL,16,F"Everybody is just passing the hot
OL,17,Fpotato and not actually addressing the
OL,18,Fproblem."
