OL,6,FMs Rathbone added she was shocked that
OL,7,F35 whistleblowers had contacted ITV
OL,8,FWales with concerns about culture in
OL,9,Fnorth Wales.
OL,11,FWhen asked if she thought bosses were
OL,12,F"wanting to keep a lid on it", she
OL,13,Fsaid: "I certainly think so. But I
OL,14,Fdon't think they're doing a very good
OL,15,Fjob."
