OL,6,FFollowing the release of a damning
OL,7,Freport into the culture at South Wales
OL,8,FFire and Rescue Service in January,
OL,9,FWelsh Government drafted in four
OL,10,Fcommissioners to oversee changes at
OL,11,Fthe service.
OL,13,FAt the start of February, the
OL,14,Fcommissioners appointed Mr Millington,
OL,15,Fthe deputy chief in the north, as the
OL,16,Finterim chief fire officer in south
OL,17,FWales.
