OL,6,FHowever, just days later, ITV revealed
OL,7,Fthat Mr Millington was at the centre
OL,8,Fof bullying allegations himself,
OL,9,Fallegations he denies.
OL,11,FMs Rathbone says she was surprised by
OL,12,Fhis appointment, saying: "We were
OL,13,Fcertainly surprised by his appointment
OL,14,Fonce we realised some of the
OL,15,Fallegations against him, and I wonder
OL,16,Fwhether the commissioners were
OL,17,Fproperly advised."
