OL,7,Fcommissioners' role in appointing Mr
OL,8,FMillington, she said: "Were they
OL,9,Freally aware? Were they told that this
OL,10,Fgentleman had these outstanding
OL,11,Fallegations against him?
OL,13,F"Or was this done by the officers and
OL,14,Fthen put to them as a recommendation?
OL,15,FI think there are alot of questions
OL,16,Faround that.
