OL,6,FMr Millington said in a statement:
OL,7,F"The vast majority of our staff come
OL,8,Fto work every day and treat each other
OL,9,Fwith dignity and respect. A small
OL,10,Fminority, however, do not.
OL,12,F"A root-and-branch transformation
OL,13,Fprogramme is underway to deliver the
OL,14,Frecommendations in the Morris review,
OL,15,Fand I applaud the colleagues who came
OL,16,Fforward and called out the poor
OL,17,Fbehaviours highlighted.
